I '''Saul Bass''' (Mayo 8, 1920 – Abril 25, 1996) metung yang Americanung [[graphic designer]] ampong talagawang pelikulang sinambut [[Oscars|Oscar]], a pikabalwan dili king kayang disenyu da reng ''title sequence'' ampong poster da reng pelikula, ampo deng logo da reng kumpanya. 

Kilub ning karera nang apat a pulung (40) banwa, megobra ya i Bass para kareng mapilan kareng pekasikat a talagawang pelikula ning Hollywood, antimo di [[Alfred Hitchcock]], [[Otto Preminger]], [[Billy Wilder]], [[Stanley Kubrick]] ampong [[Martin Scorsese]]. Kayabe ya kareng pekasikat nang [[title sequence]] ing kikimut a ginupit a papil (''animated paper cut-out'') ning takde ning adik king heroin para king pelikula nang Preminger a ''[[The Man with the Golden Arm]]'', nung nu deng credit pupulayi la ketang kaybat maging matas pangakwa (''high-angle shot'') ning skyscraper king ''[[North by Northwest]]'' nang Hitchcock, ampo ing sulat a e tuglung-tuglung (''disjointed text'') a pupulaying abe-abe ampong mikakawani king ''[[Psycho (1960 film)|Psycho]]''.

Dinisenyu nong Bass deng kapansin-pansin logo da reng kumpanya king Pangulung America, kayabe ne ing kampana ("bell") a logo ning [[American Telephone & Telegraph Company|AT&T]] anyang 1969, ampo ing "globe" logo ning [[American Telephone & Telegraph Company|AT&T]] anyang 1983 kaybat nang misalbag ning Bell System after the [[Bell System divestiture|kaybat nang misalbag ning Bell System]]. Migdisenyu ya mu namang "jetstream" logo para king [[Continental Airlines]] anyang 1968 ampong "tulip" logo  para king [[United Airlines]] anyang 1974, a meging metung kareng pekakilalang logo ning industria da reng airline king panaun a ita. Dininan neng dangalan ning [[Google]] i Saul Bass kapamilatan ning pamamili kaya king [[Google Doodle]] anyang Mayo 8, 2013.<ref>[http://ibnlive.in.com/news/watch-google-posts-a-video-doodle-for-saul-bass-93rd-birthday/390172-11.html Google Doodle]</ref> 

